Package civitas.celestis.task.lifecycle

Class CommunalScheduler

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.task.lifecycle.CommunalScheduler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Scheduler, Module
public class CommunalScheduler extends Object implements Scheduler
An asynchronous scheduler with one shared list of tasks and map of execution times. While the execution of tasks are distributed across multiple threads, only one central list of tasks and their corresponding contextual data exists.

Communal schedulers are less resilient compare to atomic implementations due to the central resources being shared across multiple threads.
